[[File:ShiningComet.jpg|thumb|right|200px|The Shining Comet]]
The '''''Shining Comet''''' was a lower class personnel transport which once traveled from [[Lanthrym]] to [[Bodrin]]. The ''Comet'' was a dingy, damp, unkempt hole of a [[Freighter/Legends|freighter]], designed to transport as many people as possible without caring for any luxuries. Recreational facilities were at an absolute minimum, although there was a viewing deck which allowed a great view of the surrounding stars.

It was on the flight from Lanthrym that [[Cermack Rustill]] boarded the ship. During the flight, [[Consolidations Unlimited]] attacked and disabled the ship, capturing both Cermack, and seven other passengers, taking them aboard the ''[[Tarnta's Fang]]''. It is unknown if this ship was then destroyed, or simply left disabled in space.

